ex01Answer.html

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html xmlns:th="http://www.thymeleaf.orf">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8">
		<title>받는쪽</title>
	</head>
	<body style="background-color:aqua">
		나는<strong th:text="${id}"></strong>의 비번을 알고 있다.<hr>
		<strong th:text="${pw}"></strong>맞지? 아하하핳!!!
	</body>
</html>
