ex02Answer.html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html xmlns:th="http://www.thymeleaf.org">
	<head><meta charset="UTF-8">
	<title>연봉</title>
	</head>
	<body style="background-color:#F5ECCE">
		<span th:text="${name}">name</span>
		<span th:text="${po}">po</span>님의 연봉은 <p>
		<span th:text="${salary}">salary</span> 만원입니다.
	</body>
</html>
